| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3242 — Recovery Inhibition (ragnarlocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: bbaa42c1-9edd-5514-ab66-4682b08cd5f3"
